Description:
   Iron Skin is a passive conditioning technique mastered by experienced
   Pugilists. Through years of repeated blows and deliberate skin-hardening
   exercises, the fighter develops a natural resistance to physical damage.
   The skin and underlying tissue become denser and more resilient, providing
   a permanent reduction in damage taken from physical attacks.

   Iron Skin is always active once learned — it does not need to be activated
   and cannot be dispelled by normal means. The conditioning is physiological
   rather than magical, meaning it persists regardless of magical suppression
   effects. Combined with the Pugilist's other defensive techniques, Iron Skin
   makes these fighters remarkably durable despite fighting without heavy armor.
